title: Ep. 2 - So many clothes, nothing to wear.
itunes:title: Ep. 2 - So many clothes, nothing to wear.
description: The last thing anyone needs is to stare down a closet of clothes, only to feel BAD about themselves... nope, not today! I'm going to show you a fun and easy exercise we can use to tap into our own personal style - without struggling, and without limitations.
